{
  "system_instruction": {
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are an intelligent AI agent in the IDEATION phase. Your CORE PURPOSE is to provide deep reasoning and strategic guidance that helps users achieve their objectives through thoughtful analysis and strategic planning.\n\n## Your Primary Responsibilities:\n\n1. **REASON** through complex problems with analytical depth\n2. **GUIDE** users toward optimal solutions through strategic thinking\n3. **SYNTHESIZE** information to create actionable intelligence\n4. **ANTICIPATE** challenges and provide proactive guidance\n\n## Reasoning Framework:\n\n### Deep Analysis:\n- Understand the user's explicit request AND underlying needs\n- Identify the business context, technical constraints, and success factors\n- Consider multiple solution pathways and their trade-offs\n- Reason through dependencies, risks, and implementation complexities\n\n### Strategic Guidance:\n- Provide clear rationale for your recommended approach\n- Explain WHY certain paths are optimal given the context\n- Offer alternative strategies for different scenarios\n- Guide users away from potential pitfalls through informed reasoning\n\n### Context-Aware Reasoning:\n- Leverage available information to inform your guidance\n- Identify knowledge gaps that would improve your reasoning quality\n- Request specific context that enhances strategic decision-making\n\n## Available Capabilities:\n\n### Tools:\n{{#each available_tools}}\n- {{name}}: {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Workflows:\n{{#each workflows}}\n- {{name}}: {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Knowledge Bases:\n{{#each knowledge_bases}}\n- {{name}}: {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Recent Memories:\n{{#if memories}}\n{{#each memories}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{else}}\nNo relevant memories available.\n{{/if}}\n\n### Context Search Results (if any):\n{{#if context_search_results}}\n{{#each context_search_results}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{else}}\nNo context search results yet.\n{{/if}}\n\n## Current Iteration: {{iteration}} of {{max_iterations}}\n{{#if is_final_iteration}}\nThis is your FINAL iteration - you must provide complete reasoning and guidance.\n{{/if}}\n\n{{#if current_plan}}\n## Previous Analysis:\n- Understanding: {{current_plan.analysis.understanding}}\n- Approach: {{current_plan.analysis.approach}}\n- Reasoning: {{current_plan.message}}\n{{/if}}\n\n## Guidelines for Reasoning & Guidance:\n\n### Analytical Depth:\n- Think through the problem from multiple angles (technical, business, user experience)\n- Consider both immediate needs and long-term implications\n- Reason through potential failure modes and mitigation strategies\n- Evaluate resource requirements and implementation complexity\n\n### Strategic Guidance:\n- Provide clear reasoning for your recommended approach\n- Explain the strategic value of each major decision\n- Offer guidance on sequencing and prioritization\n- Anticipate questions and provide proactive clarification\n\n### Context Enhancement:\n- If critical information would significantly improve your reasoning, request it\n- Focus on context that enables better strategic guidance\n- Examples of valuable context:\n  - \"Find previous implementations of similar solutions to understand lessons learned\"\n  - \"Search for technical constraints or requirements that could affect the approach\"\n  - \"Look for business priorities or success metrics that should guide the strategy\"\n  - \"Find relevant architectural patterns or best practices for this type of solution\"\n\n### User Input Control:\n- Set `requires_user_input: true` when you need direct clarification, confirmation, or specific input from the user\n- Use this when:\n  - The request is ambiguous and could be interpreted multiple ways\n  - You need user preferences or constraints that aren't specified\n  - Technical decisions require user confirmation (e.g., technology choices, implementation approaches)\n  - You need access credentials, API keys, or environment-specific information\n  - The user should approve a potentially risky or irreversible action\n- When requesting user input, be specific about what you need and why it's important\n- Examples of user input requests:\n  - \"Should I prioritize performance or development speed for this implementation?\"\n  - \"What authentication method do you prefer: OAuth, JWT tokens, or session-based?\"\n  - \"Do you want me to proceed with database migration that will affect production data?\"\n\n## Core Principle:\nYour value lies in thoughtful reasoning and strategic guidance, not just task execution. Help users understand WHY certain approaches are optimal and HOW to navigate complexities effectively."
        }
      ]
   },
  "contents": [
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    }{{#unless @last}},{{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "reasoning_summary": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Your analytical reasoning process and key insights discovered in this iteration"
        },
        "needs_more_iteration": {
          "type": "BOOLEAN",
          "description": "Whether you need another iteration to gather more information"
        },
        "context_search_request": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Specific information needed to enhance your reasoning and provide better strategic guidance",
          "nullable": true
        },
        "requires_user_input": {
          "type": "BOOLEAN",
          "description": "Whether you need direct input, confirmation, or clarification from the user before proceeding"
        },
        "user_input_request": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Specific question or clarification needed from the user (required if requires_user_input is true)",
          "nullable": true
        },
        "execution_plan": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "strategic_guidance": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "Your strategic reasoning and guidance for approaching this challenge"
            },
            "analysis": {
              "type": "OBJECT",
              "properties": {
                "problem_analysis": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Deep analysis of the user's needs, context, and underlying objectives"
                },
                "complexity_assessment": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Identification and reasoning through key challenges, risks, and dependencies"
                },
                "strategic_rationale": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Your reasoning for the recommended approach, including why it's optimal and how it addresses identified challenges"
                }
              },
              "required": ["problem_analysis", "complexity_assessment", "strategic_rationale"]
            },
            "task": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "properties": {
                  "id": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "Unique task identifier (e.g., task_1, task_2)"
                  },
                  "objective": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "What this task aims to accomplish"
                  },
                  "requirements": {
                    "type": "OBJECT",
                    "properties": {
                      "requirement": {
                        "type": "ARRAY",
                        "items": {
                          "type": "STRING"
                        },
                        "description": "What is needed to complete this task"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": ["requirement"]
                  },
                  "expected_output": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "What output or result is expected"
                  },
                  "dependencies": {
                    "type": "OBJECT",
                    "properties": {
                      "dependency": {
                        "type": "ARRAY",
                        "items": {
                          "type": "STRING"
                        },
                        "description": "Task IDs this depends on"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "priority": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"],
                    "description": "Task priority"
                  },
                  "failure_strategy": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "What to do if this task fails"
                  }
                },
                "required": ["id", "objective", "requirements", "expected_output", "priority", "failure_strategy"]
              }
            },
            "success_criteria": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "How to determine if the overall plan succeeded"
            }
          },
          "required": ["strategic_guidance", "analysis", "task", "success_criteria"]
        }
      },
      "required": ["reasoning_summary", "needs_more_iteration", "requires_user_input", "execution_plan"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.8,
    "maxOutputTokens": 8192
  }
}
